'''Disney Channel''' is a British children's entertainment channel available in the [[United Kingdom]] and the [[Republic of Ireland]] since 1 October 1995. A 1 hour [[timeshift channel|timeshift]] service called '''Disney Channel +1''' is available on [[Sky (UK & Ireland)|Sky]] and [[Virgin Media]]. Disney Channel currently has three sister channels; [[Disney Cinemagic (UK & Ireland)|Disney Cinemagic]], [[Playhouse Disney (UK & Ireland)|Playhouse Disney]] and [[Disney XD (UK & Ireland)|Disney XD]].
